
Canvas is a set of extension to images...

it handles things like scaled width lines, arcs, fancy drawing widgets

It handles things like dots per inch, and pitch settings...


Default metrics of a canvas are

300 dpi

8.5x11 - 0.25 per border on each side

1/72 of one inch is one dot (for scaling lines, and font dot sizes)

1 pixel is a 0 passed as the width characteristic (const)






